headline: AT&T aims to leverage Lumen ‘Mass Markets’ buy to bury US rivals
summary: AT&T is level set on keeping its perch as the largest fibre player in the US consumer services landscape. With its announced deal to purchase Lumen’s Mass Markets fibre business, AT&T scales up both its buildout ambitions and its convergence pool.
